\begin_layout Standard
We'll note that 
\begin_inset Formula $\frac{\abs{\left(x,y,z\right)\times\vec{v}}}{\left|\left(x,y,z\right)\right|}=\frac{\left|\left(x,y,z\right)\cdot\left|\vec{v}\right|\cdot\sin\theta\cdot\vec{n}\right|}{\left|\left(x,y,z\right)\right|}=\vec{v}\cdot\sin\theta$
